{"type":"text","timestamp":1775859138651,"sessionID":"ses_2868fbe40ffeEtJV6RkRLyNBrq","part":{"id":"prt_d7973a3cf001GrzWT0Z1Pe5nU5","messageID":"msg_d79739a0b001aNEsXkpa4SLpNZ","sessionID":"ses_2868fbe40ffeEtJV6RkRLyNBrq","type":"text","text":"## Verification Report: AR-009 — Router HTTP Reverse Proxy Core\n\n### Summary\n\nI have verified the implementation against the provided spec. Here are my findings:\n\n---\n\n### ✅ API Types Verification (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1)\n\n| Spec Requirement | Implementation Status | Details |\n|------------------|----------------------|---------|\n| **API Group** | ✅ **PASS** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` (constants.go:23, register.go:28) |\n| **API Version** | ✅ **PASS** | `v1alpha1` (constants.go:27, register.go:29) |\n| **Full APIVersion** | ✅ **PASS** | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` |\n| **AgentRuntime resource plural** | ✅ **PASS** | `agentruntimes` (constants.go:53, agentruntime_types.go:250) |\n| **CodeInterpreter resource plural** | ✅ **PASS** | `codeinterpreters` (constants.go:59, codeinterpreter_types.go:197) |\n| **SchemeGroupVersion** | ✅ **PASS** | Correctly defined in register.go:27-30 |\n| **AddToScheme** | ✅ **PASS** | Available and functional (register.go:36) |\n| **Resource() function** | ✅ **PASS** | Returns correct GroupResource (register.go:40-42) |\n| **DeepCopy functions** | ✅ **PASS** | Auto-generated in zz_generated.deepcopy.go |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Type Definitions\n\n#### AgentRuntime (agentruntime_types.go)\n- ✅ `AgentRuntimeSpec` with all required fields: Image, Resources, Env, Command, Args, WorkingDir, Ports, VolumeMounts, Volumes, ServiceAccountName, NodeSelector, Tolerations, Affinity, TTLSecondsAfterFinished, IdleTimeoutSeconds, MaxLifetimeSeconds\n- ✅ `AgentRuntimeStatus` with Phase, Conditions, SandboxID, PodName, PodIP, StartTime, CompletionTime, LastActivityTime, Message, Reason, ObservedGeneration\n- ✅ `AgentRuntimeCondition` with Type, Status, LastTransitionTime, Reason, Message\n- ✅ Phase constants: Pending, Running, Succeeded, Failed, Unknown\n- ✅ Condition types: Ready, SandboxCreated, SandboxReady, Failed\n\n#### CodeInterpreter (codeinterpreter_types.go)\n- ✅ `CodeInterpreterSpec` with Ports, Template, SessionTimeout, MaxSessionDuration, WarmPoolSize, AuthMode\n- ✅ `CodeInterpreterStatus` with Conditions and Ready\n- ✅ `CodeInterpreterCondition` with same structure as AgentRuntimeCondition\n- ✅ Protocol types: HTTP, HTTPS\n- ✅ Auth modes: picod, none\n\n---\n\n### ⚠️ Missing Implementation\n\n| Item | Status | Notes |\n|------|--------|-------|\n| **client-go library** | ❌ **MISSING** | The `client-go/` directory does not exist. This should be generated using `make gen-client` which runs `hack/update-codegen.sh` (as specified in deployment/design.md:245) |\n| **pkg/router implementation** | ❌ **MISSING** | Only `doc.go` exists; actual router HTTP reverse proxy code needs to be implemented in `cmd/router/main.go` and supporting files |\n| **hack/update-codegen.sh** | ❌ **MISSING** | Required for client generation |\n| **Makefile** | ❌ **MISSING** | Build automation not present |\n\n---\n\n### ✅ Test Results\n\n```\n$ go test -v ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\n=== RUN   TestAgentRuntimePhaseValues\n--- PASS: TestAgentRuntimePhaseValues (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestAgentRuntimeConditionTypeValues\n--- PASS: TestAgentRuntimeConditionTypeValues (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestAgentRuntimeSpec\n--- PASS: TestAgentRuntimeSpec (0.00s)\n=== RUN   TestAgentRuntimeStatus\n--- PASS: TestAgentRuntimeStatus (0.00s)\n...\nPASS\nok  \tgithub.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\t(cached)\n```\n\n**All 56 tests PASS** ✅\n\n---\n\n### Spec Compliance Summary\n\n| Category | Compliance |\n|----------|------------|\n| API Group & Version | ✅ 100% |\n| Resource Names | ✅ 100% |\n| Type Definitions | ✅ 100% |\n| Generated Code (deepcopy) | ✅ 100% |\n| Tests | ✅ 100% passing |\n| client-go library | ❌ Not generated |\n| Router implementation | ❌ Not implemented |\n\n---\n\n### Conclusion\n\nThe **API type definitions** in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` are **fully compliant** with the client-go spec. All types, constants, and generated code match the requirements.\n\nHowever, the following **need to be implemented** to complete AR-009:\n1. **client-go library** - Generate using code-generator (k8s.io/code-generator v0.34.1)\n2. **Router HTTP reverse proxy** - Implement in `cmd/router/` and `pkg/router/`\n3. **Build infrastructure** - Add Makefile and hack/update-codegen.sh","time":{"start":1775859138648,"end":1775859138648}}}
